---
title: Thyme-Roasted Turkey with Chive Mash and Gravy
description: Tonight's star-studded feast comes complete with a thyme and cranberry-glazed roast turkey, creamy mash, savoury turkey gravy and toasted almond-flecked Brussel sprouts!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/festin-haut-de-gamme-dinde-rotie-au-thym-434994f6.jpg
